name: "Opal Moon" by potentialight.art
description: @potentialight Hicetnunc Exclusive ✦ 2020 px x 2020 px 33/33 edition.  ⦿ "Opal Moon” is about the passage of time and the importance of observing the cycles that exist. The moon is such a magical object if perceived this way. It has the power to move water. It has the capacity to move you if you allow it to. New moon, plant intentions, full moon harvest endeavors. The serendipitous clock in the sky.
